head_commit.message:
Update CI scripts by split local and remote CI, update remote CI script, add logo (#129)

* Split test CI config into local (riscv64 and aarch64) and remote (x86_64) configs.

* Update remote CI configs, for better outputs and efficiency.

* Update CI configs, to make CI on `nightly` never fail.

* Add two logos.
